headline: Melissa Voeller Joins the Identity Theft Resource Center's Board of Directors
summary: Melissa Voeller of Gen Digital has joined the Board of Directors of the Identity Theft Resource Center® (ITRC), a nationally recognized nonprofit organization established to support victims of identity crime.
